(4, 'Leadership & Management', 'leadership-management', 'Develop the confidence and skills needed to lead teams, manage projects, and drive organizational success with our Leadership & Management course. This program is designed for aspiring leaders, professionals, entrepreneurs, and managers who want to strengthen their decision-making, communication, and strategic thinking abilities.\r\n\r\nThrough practical learning, real-world case studies, and expert guidance, you will learn how to motivate teams, improve workplace productivity, handle challenges effectively, and build strong leadership qualities. The course covers essential management principles, team coordination, conflict resolution, business communication, and modern leadership strategies required in today’s competitive environment.\r\n\r\nBy the end of the course, you will be equipped with the knowledge and confidence to lead with vision, inspire teams, and achieve professional growth in any industry.', '10 weeks', 'uploads/courses/1778765377.webp', NULL, '2026-05-14 07:59:37', '2026-05-14 07:59:37');

