(132, 'Silk-screen printing', 'silk-screen-printing', 'Silk-screen printing, also known as screen printing or serigraphy, is a versatile printing technique that involves transferring ink through a mesh screen onto various surfaces. This method creates vibrant, durable prints that stand the test of time.', 'posts/printing-services-in-kerala-silk-screen-printing.jpg', NULL, 42, 1, 0, '2026-03-13 00:17:00', '2026-03-25 06:47:31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
