(244, 'about us', 'about-us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 1, 1, '2026-04-20 01:44:03', '2026-05-02 06:55:42', NULL, NULL, '<p>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>Are you tired of paying high electricity bills every month? Looking for a smart solution for your home or business?<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>Welcome to Solarmaster – Kochi\'s trusted name in solar panel installation. EV charging stations, and green energy solutions since 2017.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;div style=\"font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:#173c64;margin-bottom:18px;\"&gt;<br>ABOUT US<br>&lt;/div&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>Founded in 2017, Solarmaster is a trusted solar energy company in Kochi, Kerala.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>At Solarmaster, we believe solar is the smartest move to secure your future. We supply and install high-efficiency solar panels and inverters designed to reduce dependency on high-cost electricity. You save on monthly power bills while adding long-term value and energy independence.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>We proudly work with trusted brands such as &lt;strong&gt;DMEGC&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;PowerOne&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Bosch&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Okaya&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;SunPower&lt;/strong&gt;, known for quality, performance, and support.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>At Solarmaster, we offer only top-quality, high-efficiency solar products with long-term warranty and after-sales support. We prioritize performance, durability, and trusted service that keeps your investment safe for years.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>We stay updated with the latest solar technologies so we provide the most efficient systems for homes and businesses. We proudly supply trusted and long-lasting brands such as DMEGC, PowerOne, Bosch, Okaya, SunPower and more.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;margin-bottom:14px;\"&gt;<br>Whether you are looking for solar inverters, solar panels, or battery backup systems, we provide durable and cost-effective solutions at the best prices in Kerala.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4f5f73;\"&gt;<br>&lt;span style=\"color:#d84343;font-weight:700;\"&gt;At Solarmaster Kerala&lt;/span&gt;, we offer the most trusted<br>&lt;span style=\"color:#d84343;font-weight:700;\"&gt;solar product suppliers in Kerala&lt;/span&gt;,<br>offering a wide range of high-quality products for homes and businesses.<br>&lt;/p&gt;<br>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&lt;div style=\"font-size:52px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.05;color:#16395f;margin-bottom:18px;\"&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Solar Master&lt;br&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; is a Green&lt;br&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Energy&lt;br&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Venture</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;div style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3e556e;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:18px;font-weight:600;\"&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Helping Kerala Shine Brighter with Sustainable Energy.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Located at Kochi in Ernakulam district of Kerala to provide an endurable energy solution.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&lt;h3 style=\"font-size:34px;margin-bottom:18px;font-weight:800;\"&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Why Customers Trust Us</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/h3&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;ul style=\"padding-left:18px;line-height:1.9;font-size:14px;margin:0;\"&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;li&gt;We use only top-quality, high-efficiency solar products from leading brands.&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;li&gt;We provide an integrated and durable approach for home and business needs.&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;li&gt;We follow long engineering standards to maximize power output at the lowest cost.&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;li&gt;Every product comes with strong warranty support.&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;li&gt;Our systems qualify for MNRE / KSEB subsidy approved solutions in Kerala.&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;li&gt;Our expert installation team ensures timely project completion and reliable service.&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/ul&gt;</p>', '<p>&lt;h3 class=\"offer-title\"&gt;What We Offer&lt;/h3&gt;</p><p>&lt;ul class=\"offer-list\"&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;li&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;Solar power plant installations customized for your energy needs.&lt;/p&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;li&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;Solar inverters from trusted and commercial brands.&lt;/p&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;li&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;Solar water heaters for energy-efficient heating.&lt;/p&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;li&gt;<br><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;Solar street lights, garden lights, lanterns, and roof mounted lights.&lt;/p&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;li&gt;<br><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;Solar batteries for backup power and off-grid systems.&lt;/p&gt;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;/ul&gt;</p>'),
