INSERT INTO `product_sections` (`id`, `product_id`, `title`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(70, 21, 'Solar Street Light Installation', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>Conventional electric street lights can be replaced with solar street lights. Solar street lights are sleek, compact in design and size. So the remote locations in Kerala where it is difficult get access to electricity, solar street lights are a solution for the problem.</p>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(71, 21, 'ADVANTAGES OF SOLAR STREET LIGHTS', '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Can be installed at remote places</li><li>Different capacities are available ranging from 5 W, to 50W</li><li>Electricity bill can be reduced</li><li>Water proof</li><li>Less maintenance</li><li>Our services is available in all districts of Kerala</li><li>Light sensor allows to switch on the light in dusk</li><li>Best quality solar street light at lowest price.</li></ul>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(72, 21, 'Garden Lights Installation in Kerala', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you wish to illuminate your garden in environment friendly way, the best option available is solar garden lights. It is available in different colours, sizes and shapes. You can choose the lights according to your garden.The high intensity light gives your garden premium look. Solar&nbsp; Master is one of the major solar garden lights dealer in Ernakulam, Kerala with high quality and low price.</p>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(73, 21, 'ADVANTAGES OF GARDEN LIGHTS', '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Solar garden lights are compact in size</li><li>Water resistance</li><li>No wiring is required</li><li>Works up to 12 hrs</li><li>Light sensor helps to switch on automatically in the night.</li><li>Solar garden lights can be used to decorate your house and garden</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(74, 21, 'Solar Powered Wall Mounted Lights', '<p>Solar Master has a huge collection of various types of solar energy powered wall mounted lights at lowest price and high quality. Solar wall mounted lights of three modes of function are available.</p><p>A) Sensor Mode</p><p>Solar light turns on whenever a motion is detected and turns off when there is no motion.</p><p>B) Sensor with Dim Light</p><p>Switches on automatically at night with dim light and when a motion is detected, brightness increases.</p><p>C) Auto Mode</p><p>Stores energy during day time and switch on automatically at the night.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Get a Quote</a></p>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(75, 21, 'ADVANTAGES OF SOLAR POWERED WALL MOUNTED LIGHTS', '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Compact in size.</li><li>Solar wall mounted lights can be easily installed.</li><li>Solar wall mounted lights are light weight, low cost, durable and water resistant.</li></ul>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(76, 21, 'Solar Lanterns', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>Solar lanterns are the most commonly used solar product and Solar Master is one of the leading dealer of solar lanterns in Ernakulam, Kerala.</p>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(77, 21, 'ADVANTAGES OF SOLAR LANTERNS', '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Provisions for solar charging and electrical charging are available in solar lanterns.</li><li>Solar lanterns have High intensity light</li><li>Low cost and less maintenance</li><li>Solar lanterns are easy to handle</li><li>Solar lanterns are available in different sizes and colours.</li></ul>', '2026-04-29 06:47:22', '2026-04-29 06:47:22'),
(109, 20, 'Solar Water Heater', '<p>We have two types of solar water heaters</p><ul><li>Evacuated tube</li><li>Flat plate</li></ul><p>Difference between these two depends on the design and materials of construction.</p><p>Evacuated tube is constructed with concentric borosilicate glass. Vacuum is maintained in between glass and the inner glass is mirror finished.</p><p>Flat plate collectors are made up of copper so that it gets heated fast. But the cost of construction is high and heat loss is more in flat plate than Evacuated tube collector.</p>', '2026-04-30 01:01:39', '2026-04-30 01:01:39'),
(110, 20, 'WORKING OF SOLAR WATER HEATER', '<p>Water to be heated enters into the collecting tanks through the inlet and water comes in contact with sunlight through the tubes. The water reaches to a temperature of 80 to 85 degree Celsius and the hot water is returned to the outlet through collecting tank</p>', '2026-04-30 01:01:39', '2026-04-30 01:01:39'),
(111, 20, 'Specifications', '<ol><li>Solar water heaters of various capacities are available – 100, 150,200,250,300 litres per day.</li><li>Material of construction</li></ol><ul><li>Inner and outer tanks are composed of food grade stainless steel.</li><li>Vacuum tubes are made of boring silicate glass covered with black coating</li><li>Stands are available in both aluminium and galvanised iron</li></ul><p>Solar Master is very conscious about the uality of products so our quality control team ensures that the customer gets the best product available in the world at a low cost. Our excellent servicing is available throughout Kerala.</p>', '2026-04-30 01:01:39', '2026-04-30 01:01:39'),
(112, 20, 'ADVANTAGES OF SOLAR WATER HEATER', '<ul><li>Solar Water heaters can reduce electricity bills</li><li>Compact in size</li><li>Maintenance free</li><li>It can save our valuable time</li><li>Long life span</li><li>Long term warranty</li><li>Gives &nbsp;better performance even on cloudy days</li><li>Ensure minimum heat loss to surrounding</li><li>Can handle hard water also</li><li>Can be connected with pressure pumps</li></ul>', '2026-04-30 01:01:39', '2026-04-30 01:01:39'),
(129, 19, 'Why Solar Panel Cleaning is Essential', '<p>Even the <strong>best solar panels in India</strong> lose efficiency when they’re dirty. Dust, bird droppings, leaves, and pollution reduce sunlight absorption, directly affecting your electricity generation.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Dirty panels can lose up to 30% of their output</strong>.</p><p>If your solar system isn’t delivering the savings you expected, it might just need a proper cleaning.<br>That’s where <strong>SolarMaster Kochi</strong> steps in.</p>', '2026-04-30 01:17:52', '2026-04-30 01:17:52'),
(130, 19, 'Key Benefits of Regular Solar Panel Cleaning', '<ul><li>Boosts energy production</li><li>Improves return on investment (ROI)</li><li>Keeps your system warranty valid</li><li>Avoids long-term wear or damage</li><li>Supports Kerala’s clean energy goals</li></ul>', '2026-04-30 01:17:52', '2026-04-30 01:17:52'),
(131, 19, 'How We Clean Solar Panels', '<p>Our expert team follows a <strong>safe and efficient solar panel cleaning procedure</strong>:</p><ol><li><strong>Inspection</strong> – We check for cracks, debris, or electrical issues.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>RO Water Wash</strong> – Clean, demineralized water used for safe surface cleaning.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Soft Cloth Drying</strong> – No chemicals or hard brushes that could harm your panels.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Output Testing</strong> – Measure the improvement in energy generation post-cleaning.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Report &amp; Recommendations</strong> – Maintenance tips, service logs, and upgrade advice.<br>&nbsp;</li></ol><p>This service is perfect for:&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Residential rooftop solar panels</strong></li><li><strong>Commercial solar plants in Kochi</strong></li><li><strong>Industrial solar installations across Kerala</strong><br>&nbsp;</li></ul>', '2026-04-30 01:17:52', '2026-04-30 01:17:52'),
(132, 19, 'Technical Services We Offer', '<p>Solar panels are just one part of your system. SolarMaster offers full <strong>technical support for solar power plants in Kerala</strong>, including:</p><ul><li>Inverter troubleshooting &amp; firmware updates</li><li>Battery health checks (for off-grid &amp; hybrid systems)</li><li>AC/DC wiring inspection</li><li>Net meter support &amp; connection review</li><li>Solar lightning arrester &amp; surge protection audits</li><li>System alignment for seasonal performance</li></ul><p>We support all major brands, including <strong>Waaree, Vikram, Loom Solar, Fronius, ABB, SMA, EXIDE, and more</strong>.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Serving All Areas in Kochi &amp; Nearby</strong></h3><p>SolarMaster provides <strong>solar panel maintenance in Kochi,</strong> including areas like:<br><strong>Aluva, Edappally, Vyttila, Kakkanad, Tripunithura, Kalamassery</strong>, and more.</p><p>We also offer <strong>annual maintenance contracts (AMC)</strong> and <strong>emergency support for commercial solar panels in Kerala</strong>.</p>', '2026-04-30 01:17:52', '2026-04-30 01:17:52'),
(192, 22, 'Solar Inverter Supply in Kochi', '<p>Inverters are the heart of every solar powered system. Solar Master has the most reliable, efficient and smart inverter solutions for homes and businesses across Kerala.</p><p>We supply premium solar inverters ranging from residential systems to large industrial and commercial systems. From the day of installation, Solar Master also provides project support, service and technical support.</p><p>Solar Master deals with both off-grid as well as on-grid solar inverters. Our products are available at the best prices and include top quality imported brands.</p><p>Our products are highly efficient with 100% pure sine wave output with all certifications. We use MPPT charge controllers for premium maximum output.</p><p>Solar Master supplies these products with warranty of minimum 5 years, extendable to 25 years.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '2026-04-30 03:38:01', '2026-04-30 03:38:01'),
(193, 22, 'ON GRID / OFF GRID INVERTER', '<p>Converts DC current produced by Solar panels into AC current with maximum efficiency. The solar On grid inverter transmits the excess current produced by Solar system to the electricity board grid and vice versa. Solar Master has the most efficient inverters with fixed unity power factor which ensures the output voltage and current in perfect manner. On grid solar inverters have the following features<br>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Extended warranty up to 25 years</li><li>Online monitoring through mobile application and computer</li><li>Easy maintenance<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p>OFF GRID TIED INVERTER</p><p>Off grid inverter ensures uninterrupted power supply all the time with the help of battery bank. It is also useful even in remote areas. Solar Master supplies the best quality off-grid inverters available in the market at the lowest price, capacities from 500VA to 10VA.</p>', '2026-04-30 03:38:01', '2026-04-30 03:38:01'),
(194, 22, 'Solar Batteries Supply in Kerala', '<p>In an <strong>off-grid solar power system</strong>, solar batteries play a key role by storing the extra energy produced by solar panels during the day. This stored power can be used at night or during power cuts, ensuring an uninterrupted supply of electricity.</p><p>At <strong>Solar Master Kochi</strong>, we supply <strong>high-quality solar batteries</strong> from leading brands at the <strong>lowest prices in Kerala</strong>.</p><h3>&nbsp;Our Solar Battery Brands</h3><ul><li>We offer trusted battery brands such as:</li><li><strong>Exide</strong></li><li><strong>Luminous</strong></li><li>And other top-quality manufacturers</li></ul><p>Each battery comes with a <strong>minimum 5-year warranty</strong> (and more, if applicable), giving you complete peace of mind.</p><h3>&nbsp;Types of Solar Batteries Available</h3><p>We provide two main types of batteries for solar power systems:</p><p><strong>Lead-Acid Batteries</strong> – Affordable and widely used, ideal for residential solar setups.</p><p><strong>Lithium-Ion Batteries</strong> – Longer lifespan, lightweight, and low maintenance, perfect for advanced solar systems.</p>', '2026-04-30 03:38:01', '2026-04-30 03:38:01'),
(195, 22, 'LITHIUM IRON BATTERY', '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Mostly used for medium and large capacity usages.</li><li>Battery life about 4 to 8 years.</li><li>Has 2,000 to 3000 discharge cycles.</li><li>Cheapest battery.</li></ul><p>LITHIUM IRON BATTERY</p><ul><li>Compact in size.</li><li>Lightweight.</li><li>Less charging time.</li><li>It can last up to 10 years.</li><li>5000 to 7000 discharge cycles.</li><li>Low maintenance.</li></ul><h3>Why Choose Solar Master for Solar Batteries in Kochi?<br>&nbsp;</h3><p>Supply of <strong>C10-rated batteries</strong>, best for solar power systems</p><p>A large number of successful deliveries in <strong>Ernakulam, Kottayam, and Thrissur</strong></p><p>Fast delivery and installation support across Kerala</p><p>Expert guidance to choose the right battery for your energy needs</p>', '2026-04-30 03:38:01', '2026-04-30 03:38:01'),
(226, 17, 'Residential EV Charging Stations Installer in Kochi', '<p>SolarMaster offers custom home EV charger installation for all electric car models. We ensure your charger fits your vehicle and your home’s electrical setup.</p><ul><li>&nbsp;Safe and professional installation</li><li>&nbsp;Works with all popular electric cars</li><li>&nbsp;No major upgrades needed</li><li>&nbsp;Option to connect with solar panels</li></ul><h3>Why Choose SolarMaster in Kochi?</h3><ul><li>24/7 charging at home</li><li>Save money on fuel and power</li><li>Increase your property’s value</li><li>Be ready for more EVs in the future</li></ul><p>We are local experts in residential EV charger installation in Kochi. Whether you drive a Tata Nexon EV, MG ZS EV, BYD, or any other brand, we have you covered.</p><p>Contact SolarMaster – Your EV charger installer in Kochi<br>Get a free home survey and consultation today!</p><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Contact Today!</a></p>', '2026-04-30 06:21:51', '2026-04-30 06:21:51'),
(227, 17, 'Commercial EV Charger Installer in Kerala', '<p>With more EVs on the road, it’s the perfect time for businesses across Kerala to become EV-friendly.<br>SolarMaster helps you install commercial EV charging stations that attract customers, boost your brand, and support clean energy.</p><h3>&nbsp;Ideal for:</h3><ul><li>Hotels and resorts</li><li>Shopping malls and retail outlets</li><li>Apartment complexes and gated communities</li><li>Hospitals and clinics</li><li>Corporate offices and IT parks</li><li>Fuel stations and highway rest stops</li></ul><h3>&nbsp;Our Services Include:</h3><ul><li>Site inspection and load analysis</li><li>Supply and installation of BIS-certified EV chargers</li><li>Solar system integration (optional)</li><li>Real-time tracking and reporting</li><li>Help with government EV subsidies and permits</li></ul><p>Turn your property into an EV charging hub – attract EV drivers, increase footfall, and support green mobility.</p><p>Contact SolarMaster – Trusted EV charger installer in Kerala<br>Get a free site survey and consultation today!</p>', '2026-04-30 06:21:51', '2026-04-30 06:21:51'),
(228, 17, 'Our Process – From Inquiry to Installation', '<h4>Smooth &amp; Transparent EV Charger Installation Process with SolarMaster</h4><p>At <strong>SolarMaster</strong>, we make <strong>EV charger installation in Kerala</strong> simple and hassle-free. Here’s how we work:</p><ol><li><strong>Initial Consultation</strong><br>We discuss your EV type, location, and preferences to understand what’s best for you.</li><li><strong>Site Survey</strong><br>Our team checks your electrical setup and identifies the best spot for the charger.</li><li><strong>Proposal &amp; Quotation</strong><br>You’ll receive a clear cost estimate with all details included—no hidden charges.</li><li><strong>Installation</strong><br>We complete the setup in <strong>1 to 3 days</strong>, depending on the work required.</li><li><strong>Testing &amp; Training</strong><br>We test the charger, show you how it works, and answer all your questions.</li><li><strong>After-Sales Support</strong><br>We’re here for maintenance, upgrades, and ongoing support whenever needed.</li></ol><p><strong>Trusted EV charger installer in Kerala</strong><br>&nbsp;Contact SolarMaster today for a <strong>free consultation and site visit</strong>.</p>', '2026-04-30 06:21:51', '2026-04-30 06:21:51'),
(229, 17, 'Exclusive Partnership with EXICOM', '<p>SolarMaster is an authorized partner of EXICOM, one of India’s leading EV charging equipment manufacturers.</p><p>We supply and install EXICOM chargers known for:</p><ul><li>BIS &amp; safety certifications</li><li>Smart-grid compatibility</li><li>Reliable performance for homes and businesses</li></ul><p>Whether you need a residential EV charger or a commercial charging station, EXICOM products deliver long-term value and efficiency.</p><h3>&nbsp;Transparent Pricing &amp; Subsidy Support</h3><p>EV charger installation costs depend on:</p><ul><li>Charger type and features</li><li>Site conditions and electrical load</li><li>Integration with solar (if needed)</li></ul><p>With SolarMaster, you get:</p><ul><li>Competitive, upfront pricing</li><li>No hidden costs</li><li>Help with government EV subsidies (when available in Kerala)</li></ul><p><strong>Contact SolarMaster for expert advice and a free consultation on installing an EXICOM EV charger in Kerala.</strong></p>', '2026-04-30 06:21:51', '2026-04-30 06:21:51'),
(230, 17, 'Investment Opportunities in EV Charging Infrastructure', '<p>If you own land or commercial spaces near highways, offices, or public areas, installing EV chargers can create passive revenue streams.</p><p>Benefits for Investors:</p><ul><li>Fast-growing EV adoption in Kerala</li><li>Government-backed incentives</li><li>Low-maintenance and long-lasting infrastructure</li><li>Higher property utility and resale value</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Explore investment options with SolarMaster. Schedule a consultation.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Get a Quote</a></p>', '2026-04-30 06:21:51', '2026-04-30 06:21:51'),
(231, 17, 'Why Choose SolarMaster?', '<ul><li>&nbsp;Kerala’s trusted name for solar and EV solutions</li><li>&nbsp;3000+ completed solar and EV projects</li><li>&nbsp;An expert team of engineers and technicians</li><li>&nbsp;Official partners with ABB, Exicom, Delta, and SMA</li><li>&nbsp;End-to-end support from design to installation</li></ul><p>Future mobility is electric, and SolarMaster helps you be part of it.<br>Whether you’re a homeowner, a commercial property owner, or an investor, we provide installation of <strong>top-quality EV charging stations in Kochi and across Kerala</strong>.</p>', '2026-04-30 06:21:51', '2026-04-30 06:21:51'),
(238, 16, 'How On- Grid Solar Power Plants Work in Kochi', '<p>When you choose solar master one of the key components is the <strong>grid-connected inverter</strong>. This device converts the <strong>direct current (DC)</strong> generated by your solar panels into <strong>alternating current (AC)</strong>, the form of electricity used in homes and businesses.</p><p>An <strong>energy meter</strong> records the electricity produced by your solar system. If your solar panels generate more power than you consume, the <strong>excess electricity is automatically exported</strong> to the <strong>KSEB main power grid</strong> through a <strong>bi-directional energy meter</strong>.</p><p>This smart meter tracks your home’s electricity usage and shows how much energy you’ve supplied back to the grid. In return, you can enjoy credits on your bill, reducing your overall electricity costs.</p><p>With <strong>solar power plant installations in Kochi</strong>, you’re not only cutting down your monthly expenses but also contributing to a greener and more sustainable Kerala.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Get a Quote</a></p>', '2026-04-30 07:02:23', '2026-04-30 07:02:23'),
(239, 16, 'ADVANTAGES OF ON GRID SOLAR POWER PLANT', '<p>Installing an on-grid power plant in kochi comes with many benefits for homeowners and businesses. Here are the key advantages:</p><h3>1. No Need for Batteries</h3><p>On-grid solar systems work directly with the KSEB power grid, which means they don’t require batteries. This eliminates the recurring cost of replacing batteries, making it more affordable in the long run.</p><h3>2. Low Maintenance</h3><p>Since an on-grid solar power plant has no moving parts and no batteries, the <strong>maintenance cost is very low</strong>. Once installed, it runs smoothly for years with minimal servicing.</p><h3>3. Faster Return on Investment</h3><p>One of the biggest advantages is the <strong>quick payback period</strong>. The initial investment can usually be recovered within <strong>4 to 5 years</strong> through savings on electricity bills.</p><h3>4. Zero Electricity Bill</h3><p>With net metering, any extra solar power your system produces is exported to the KSEB grid. This can reduce your monthly electricity bill to <strong>almost zero</strong>.</p><h3>5. More Affordable Than Off-Grid Systems</h3><p>Compared to off-grid solar plants, <strong>on-grid solar systems are cheaper</strong> because they don’t require costly batteries. This makes them the best choice for cities like Kochi with a reliable power supply.</p>', '2026-04-30 07:02:23', '2026-04-30 07:02:23'),
(240, 16, 'Off Grid Solar Power Plants', '<p>If you live in an area with frequent power cuts or in a remote location without a stable electricity supply, an <strong>off-grid solar power plant in Kochi</strong> is the best solution.</p><p>At <strong>Solar Master</strong>, we are one of the leading dealers of <strong>off-grid solar systems in Kochi and Ernakulam district</strong>, with successful projects completed across Kerala – especially in <strong>Ernakulam, Kottayam, and Thrissur</strong>.</p><h3>&nbsp;How Off-Grid Solar Systems Work</h3><ul><li>During the day, solar panels generate electricity that powers your home or business.</li><li>Any extra power produced is stored in <strong>batteries</strong>.</li><li>At night or during power cuts, this stored energy is used to run your appliances without interruption.</li></ul><p>This makes off-grid solar systems ideal for areas where reliable power is a challenge.</p><h3>&nbsp;Why Choose Solar Master for Off-Grid Solar in Kochi?</h3><ul><li>Trusted solar dealer with years of experience</li><li>Completed multiple successful installations across Kerala</li><li>High-quality solar panels and battery systems</li><li>Customized solutions to match your energy needs</li></ul><p>With <strong>off-grid solar power plants in Kochi</strong>, you get complete energy independence and peace of mind, even during long power outages.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Get a Quote</a></p>', '2026-04-30 07:02:23', '2026-04-30 07:02:23'),
(241, 16, 'THE BENEFITS THAT WE OFFER', '<p>Installing an <strong>off-grid solar systems in Kochi</strong> gives you complete freedom from power cuts and rising electricity costs. Here are the major advantages:</p><h4>&nbsp;Key Benefits</h4><ul><li><strong>Complete Energy Independence</strong> – No need to rely on KSEB or the main power grid.</li><li><strong>Stable Power Supply</strong> – Voltage drops and grid fluctuations will not affect your appliances.</li><li><strong>Lower Electricity Bills</strong> – Use free solar energy during the day and store power at night.</li><li><strong>Eco-Friendly</strong> – 100% clean energy, with no harm to the environment.</li></ul><h4>&nbsp;Quality Components &amp; Expert Installation</h4><p>At <strong>Solar Master</strong>, we use only <strong>world-class, high-quality components</strong> for our off-grid solar systems. Our <strong>skilled engineers and technicians</strong> ensure timely and efficient installation for every project.</p><h4>&nbsp;Residential, Commercial &amp; Industrial Projects</h4><p>We provide customized <strong>off-grid solar solutions</strong> for:</p><ul><li>Homes</li><li>Shops and offices</li><li>Factories and industries</li></ul><p>Every product comes with a <strong>long warranty period</strong>, giving you complete peace of mind.</p><h4>&nbsp;Affordable Solar Solutions Across Kerala</h4><p>From <strong>design to execution</strong>, our services cover all stages of the project at the <strong>lowest possible cost</strong>. We have successfully installed off-grid solar plants across Kerala, including <strong>Ernakulam, Kottayam, and Thrissur</strong>.</p>', '2026-04-30 07:02:23', '2026-04-30 07:02:23'),
(242, 16, 'Government Solar Subsidy Under PM Surya Ghar – Make Solar Affordable in Kerala', '<p>At SolarMaster Kochi, we leverage the <strong>PM Surya Ghar Muft Bijli Yojana</strong> to bring you deep savings on rooftop solar installations. This flagship central scheme empowers homeowners with <strong>direct subsidy (Central Financial Assistance, CFA)</strong> for systems up to 3 kW, enabling cleaner, greener energy at much lower cost.</p><h3><strong>What is the PM Surya Ghar Subsidy?</strong></h3><ul><li>Under this scheme, residential households are eligible for a subsidy of <strong>60 % of the benchmark cost</strong> for solar systems up to <strong>2 kW</strong> and <strong>40 % for the incremental cost</strong> between 2 kW and 3 kW.</li><li>No subsidy beyond 3 kW for residential users.</li><li>The benchmark cost has been set at <strong>₹30,000 per kW</strong> for up to 2 kW and <strong>₹18,000 per kW</strong> for the additional 1 kW (for the 2–3 kW portion).</li><li>This translates into typical subsidy amounts such as:<br> • ₹30,000 for 1 kW<br> • ₹60,000 for 2 kW<br> • ₹78,000 for 3 kW</li></ul><h3><strong>Government Support in Kerala</strong></h3><p>Through the <strong>MNRE Rooftop Solar Program</strong> and <strong>PM-KUSUM scheme</strong>, the government offers up to <strong>40% subsidy</strong> for residential users. Additional benefits are available for farmers to promote solar-powered pumps and equipment. Some categories, such as BPL households, may even qualify for free installations under state programs.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Get a Quote</a></p>', '2026-04-30 07:02:23', '2026-04-30 07:02:23'),
(243, 16, 'Who Is Eligible to Avail the Subsidy?', '<p>To benefit from this solar subsidy scheme:</p><ul><li>You must be an <strong>Indian citizen</strong> and a <strong>residential household owner</strong>.<br>&nbsp;</li><li>You should have a <strong>valid electricity connection</strong> in your name.<br>&nbsp;</li><li>The roof should be structurally suitable for solar panel installation.<br>&nbsp;</li><li>You must <strong>not have already availed a subsidy under another residential rooftop solar scheme</strong>.<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><h3><strong>How the Subsidy Gets Disbursed</strong></h3><ol><li><strong>Register on the National Portal</strong> – Visit <strong>pmsuryaghar.gov.in</strong>, choose your state and DISCOM, and complete registration.</li><li><strong>Submit Application &amp; Choose Vendor</strong> – After registration, select an impaneled vendor and submit the requisite documents.</li><li><strong>Feasibility &amp; DISCOM Approval</strong> – Your DISCOM inspects the plan and grants feasibility.</li><li><strong>Installation &amp; Inspection</strong> – The vendor installs, and the system is inspected.</li><li><strong>Subsidy Release</strong> – Once approved and commissioned, the subsidy is credited to your bank account or deducted from the invoice.</li></ol><p>Typically, the subsidy is paid <strong>within 30 days</strong> of commissioning.<br><strong>Government-Backed Subsidy: PM Surya Ghar – Muft Bijli Yojana</strong></p><p>Under the <strong>PM Surya Ghar scheme</strong>, homeowners can avail <strong>Central Financial Assistance (CFA)</strong> on rooftop solar installations:</p><ul><li>For systems up to <strong>2 kW</strong>, subsidy = <strong>60%</strong> of benchmark cost</li><li>For the incremental capacity between 2–3 kW, subsidy = <strong>40%</strong></li><li>No CFA subsidy beyond 3 kW for residential consumers</li><li>Benchmark costs: ₹50,000 per kW for first 2 kW; ₹45,000 for the additional kW</li><li>Valid till <strong>March 31, 2027</strong></li><li>You must register via the <strong>pmsuryaghar.gov.in portal</strong>, choose a vendor, and submit documents via the portal</li><li>After installation and DISCOM approval, the subsidy amount gets credited or adjusted</li></ul>', '2026-04-30 07:02:23', '2026-04-30 07:02:23'),
(244, 18, 'Essential Protection for Kerala’s Lightning-Prone Regions', '<p>Kerala’s frequent lightning activity makes lightning protection a critical safety measure. SolarMaster’s lightning arresters are installed to:</p><ul><li>Minimise the risk of electrical fires and surges</li><li>Protect sensitive home and industrial equipment</li><li>Ensure operational continuity in commercial and industrial setups</li><li>Safeguard rooftop solar systems and inverters</li></ul><h3><strong>System Overview</strong></h3><p>Lightning arresters from SolarMaster provide a direct, low-impedance path for lightning currents to safely discharge into the ground, preventing structural and electrical damage. Our systems are compliant with Indian and international safety codes.</p><h3><strong>Installation Services</strong></h3><p>Our installation process ensures a secure and regulation-compliant system:</p><ol><li><strong>Site Assessment: </strong>Technical evaluation of structure, terrain, and electrical layout</li><li><strong>System Design and Product Selection: </strong>Customized system configuration based on the site assessment</li><li><strong>Installation: </strong>Grounding system, lightning rod, and conductor mesh installation</li><li><strong>Testing and Commissioning: </strong>Ground resistance verification and functional inspection</li><li><strong>Documentation and Support: </strong>System report and basic maintenance guidelines</li></ol><p><a href=\"http://www.solarmaster.in/contact-us/\">Get a Quote</a></p>', '2026-05-01 02:04:08', '2026-05-01 02:04:08'),
(245, 18, 'Professional Maintenance Services', '<p>SolarMaster offers scheduled and on-demand maintenance for lightning protection systems:</p><ul><li>Resistance testing of the earthing system</li><li>Visual inspection and cleaning of conductor pathways</li><li>Replacement of worn components</li><li>Pre-monsoon system checks<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Key Advantages of SolarMaster</strong></p><ul><li>Headquartered in Kochi with active operations across Kerala</li><li>MNRE and KSEB-approved team of certified installers</li><li>More than 3500 installations delivered</li><li>Use of high-performance, certified components</li><li>Dedicated after-sales and maintenance support</li></ul><p><strong>Client Support and Service Coverage</strong></p><p>SolarMaster provides end-to-end service for both new installations and system upgrades. We cover major regions including Kochi, Ernakulam, Thrissur, Calicut, Trivandrum, and other parts of Kerala.</p><p>For consultation, technical assessment, or maintenance scheduling</p>', '2026-05-01 02:04:08', '2026-05-01 02:04:08'),
(246, 18, 'Product Range', '<p><strong>Residential Applications</strong></p><ul><li>Compact lightning arresters for home rooftops</li><li>Aluminium and copper variants available</li><li>Rust-resistant, weather-proof components</li><li>Compatible with solar installations</li></ul><p><strong>High-Rise and Commercial Buildings</strong></p><ul><li>Complete rooftop and façade coverage</li><li>Integrated conductor mesh and ground rods</li><li>Ideal for schools, hospitals, apartments, and offices</li></ul>', '2026-05-01 02:04:08', '2026-05-01 02:04:08'),
(247, 18, 'Industrial Applications', '<ul><li>High-voltage 15kV lightning arresters</li><li>Suitable for factories, cold storage units, and warehouses</li><li>Designed for heavy-duty performance and long-term reliability&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Solar Panel Installations</strong></p><ul><li>Surge protection for solar PV modules, inverters, and batteries</li><li>Compatible with both on-grid and off-grid solar systems</li><li>Designed to protect your solar infrastructure investment</li></ul>', '2026-05-01 02:04:08', '2026-05-01 02:04:08'),
(248, 18, 'Technology Standards and Safety Assurance', '<p>SolarMaster exclusively uses <strong>conventional lightning protection systems</strong> that are compliant with BIS standards. We avoid Early Streamer Emission (ESE) systems as they are legally restricted and not recommended by Indian regulatory authorities.</p><p>Conventional systems:</p><ul><li>Offer passive protection by safely diverting lightning</li><li>Ensure stable long-term performance</li><li>Are recognized and accepted by safety codes and inspections<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Component highlights:</p><ul><li>Den brand lightning arresters</li><li>Copper-bonded earth rods and support hardware</li></ul>', '2026-05-01 02:04:08', '2026-05-01 02:04:08'),
(249, 18, 'Conventional vs. ESE Lightning Protection', '<p>Conventional lightning arresters provide a safe, low-impedance path for lightning currents, ensuring a reliable and effective protection system. In contrast, ESE lightning arresters are banned due to their controversial approach, which proactively attracts lightning strikes. By choosing conventional arresters from SolarMaster, you ensure the safety of your property without the risks associated with ESE systems.</p>', '2026-05-01 02:04:08', '2026-05-01 02:04:08');

